snippet: Mirim Lee of South Korea won the second title of her rookie L.P.G.A. Tour season, shooting a five-under-par 69 in the final round to capture the Reignwood Classic at Beijing by two strokes over Caroline Hedwall (73).
abstract: Mirim Lee of South Korea wins second title of her rookie LPGA Tour season, capturing the Reignwood Classic at Beijing; other golf news noted.
lead_paragraph: Mirim Lee of South Korea won the second title of her rookie L.P.G.A. Tour season, shooting a five-under-par 69 in the final round to capture the Reignwood Classic at Beijing by two strokes over Caroline Hedwall (73).
